<exercise number="32"><statement><p>The owner of the Koffee Shop pours the remainder of her old house blend, which is 30% Colombian beans, into a 50-pound bin, and fills it up with her new house blend, which is 25% Colombian beans. Let <m>h</m> stand for the number of pounds of the old house blend. Write algebraic expressions to answer the questions below.
